Package: reproducr
Title: Drafting and Publishing Reproducible Scientific Articles with R
        Markdown
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Julia",
           family = "Schulte-Cloos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "julia.schulte-cloos@eui.eu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7223-3602"))
Description: The `reproducr` package allows users without any prior knowledge of R Markdown to implement reproducible research practices in their scientific workflows. It provides an integrated Rmd-framework that is fully optimized for the explorative research stage and the research dissemination stage.
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.14) - http://pandoc.org
